name: MISTY MOUNTAINTOP 01
description:
St. Walburg, Sudtirol, Northern Italy.

Way up in the high mountains where families lived for generations and few come to visit.  The sturdy old cottages stand distinguished and proud. Far from the city, the silence is haunting, but make way for distant cowbells along the hillside.  

Photograph 
By RogueInfini
